Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:04.98,Titel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1010A4&\pos(990,615)}Faceless One
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satsuki Kazuma and his family were murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now tell how.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is the late Kazuma’s wife, Chou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For her crime, she was incarcerated immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept responsibility for my crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.96,Titel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1010A4&\pos(990,615)}Part the First
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:33.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}The blue moon illuminated
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:37.70,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}your wandering shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:42.20,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I could never tell you all I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:47.12,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,250)}It was so very frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:51.00,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}I think about your faked smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.63,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}and forget all the hot tears we shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.30,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}What do these empty husks,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:04.14,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}those empty eyes of yours, reflect, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:09.35,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}The transient quarter moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.52,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,100)}hides in a rift in the clouds,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.90,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(100,300)}as darkness seeps up from the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:18.36,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}Tell me the truth, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.53,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,300)}Are you so despondent
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:24.99,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}that you still sit alone, sighing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the case is solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you’ve likely surmised, I am a fellow prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a medicine seller by trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a rather rude customer, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that the pills I sold him did nothing for his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came at me with accusations of fraud and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Personally, the very belief that medicine alone\Ncan cure one’s ailments does not sit well with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.49,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ineffective medicine is\Nrendered such by one’s own lack of belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are held together by a common\Nthread, like sardines hung out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I told him that, though, he\Nscreamed at me to return his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s when the authorities arrived on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.47,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m most embarrassed that a\Ncustomer should put me in such a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, or are sardines dried on sticks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man and woman should not share the same cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, at any rate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you’re set to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,well yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The populace is abuzz with rumors of your crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou, the devil-woman who killed a samurai’s entire\Nhouse, including her own husband and father-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how they refer to me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, it was a rather heinous crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Four people hung from a plum tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn’t how it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a dreadful fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s wrong, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it, now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I’ve forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forgotten, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, rumors develop quickly indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you did it is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooked in miso or cured with salt, a fish is a fish, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You make no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe a woman could do this alone, is my point.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.34,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay it no heed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is merely a tool for my trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no witnesses and no physical\Nevidence, just your own admission of guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the details are quite vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth be told, Ochou-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not believe that you acted alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that it was the work of a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mononoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that ring any bells with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No,{\alpha&HFF&} none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.26,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you understand, people\Nalways have a certain air about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A certain expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not seem like a woman\Nbound for the gallows in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my white kimono distinguishes me as such.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your jailor determines how you dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is of more concern to me than your garb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I’m trying to say is that you seem an\Nentirely different person from the normal Ochou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could not possibly know how\NI act under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a simple medicine seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I’m a criminal right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.34,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing{,} it can speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I’ve met this sort of Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don’t be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn’t anything strange like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.07,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are safe as long as you stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re most suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, she was possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my belief, though, that I would\Nhave to break those bars to reveal your Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you would
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,come
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Witness the Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren’t a Mononoke’s true Form?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting in my way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be safe as long as you stay in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you believe this place holds you, it is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not wish to leave, it will become a fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.14,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wish to return to that place again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind is far more frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely there must be kind Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what she said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infinite providence lies with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wander now, in search of your Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won’t follow us for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the ridiculous rumors must have shocked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As that man said, I am a Mononoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mononoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born to free you from prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sake! Sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to bring me more sake! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I—I’m sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san, just get us some more sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a worthless wife you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lazy girl, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, whyever did you take her in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her mother begged me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your first wife hadn’t hung herself, would\Nyou ever have accepted her into your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she’s a pretty good cook,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.41,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and good in bed, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh stop, you’re just terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wished to purge itself of the rage\Nthat was building up like a poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Poison?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you thing it strange to\Nhear a Mononoke speak of poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sensation…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that sensation, I was able to stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over and over again, you saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.14,0:12:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must we return?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, we must.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will soon be pursued.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not want to go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are set to be hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:13:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your appeals are exhausted.\NYou are truly on the brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go back there…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all the same, whether I stay or go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not return, you will be\Nrunning from your crime all your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are found, you will be executed on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be easier, I’m sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man in the prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it that man who put such thoughts in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I simply do not wish to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you’re…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I am not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I do hold Shape and Form similar to that of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot remove my mask,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can sing and dance and do\Neverything necessary to provide for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, be my wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain you want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a convicted criminal as a wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you accept?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us be wed immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochou, today we start our new lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, look! This is my bride!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my beautiful Ochou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m astounded that Ochou-san agreed to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so jealous! So jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,200)}Congratulations! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, they’re such a rowdy bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.45,0:15:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re all so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They’ve always been around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.28,0:15:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.58,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You simply did not notice them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:43.08,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So jealous! So jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have all protected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:46.46,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Congratulations! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People tend to forget how many people they have met,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and how many of them have helped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, though, it will be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will be your reason for living!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our vows are completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We two are now as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hid myself, so as not to interrupt your taking of vows.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I merely wish to express my\Ngratitude and extend my best wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is changing for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can finally hold my head high as I visit\Nthe graves of my ancestors, the Umezawake clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,should really pay your respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were born exceptionally beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your appearance carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you will be able to marry into a wealthy\Nfamily, in spite of your humble upbringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good girl. Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! You must not show me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, {\alpha&HFF&}yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.15,0:18:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, {\alpha&HFF&}yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes, {\alpha&HFF&}yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.11,0:18:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite a wonderful play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed it very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.66,0:18:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.37,0:18:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The character for “face” can also be read as “exterior.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The human face is nothing more than its exterior appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I accept this face, it is quite easy to make it my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I see your mask has changed yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where is your real face?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.06,0:19:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This new life I’d finally gained…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s collapsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a play the Mononoke created to deceive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be hiding something.\NSomething he needed you not to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wears a mask to hide his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he hiding from you, that he required such a play?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You who have forgotten your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mononoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me {\alpha&HFF&}your Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.94,0:21:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me your Form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:10.03,Titel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,590)\fs70\c&H1010A4&}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:19.42,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}Without you, I just can’t smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.55,0:21:30.47,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I walk this banal town,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:36.56,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}feeling such intense emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:42.94,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I know that if I could treasure them and live on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:52.24,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I would need nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.91,0:22:00.42,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}The summer flowers that bloomed in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.42,0:22:06.72,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}Come falling down, dancing in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:10.05,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}I can barely recall the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.05,0:22:13.35,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}where they all came tumbling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:24.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(300,300)}so what I can still recall is all the more precious.
